  "grammarSections": [
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Vosotros Imperative Forms", "nl": "Vosotros Gebiedende Wijs" },
      "content": {
        "en": "The **vosotros** imperative (used in Spain for informal plural 'you') is formed from the infinitive by replacing the final **-r** with **-d**:\n\n**hablar → hablad** (speak!)\n**comer → comed** (eat!)\n**vivir → vivid** (live!)\n\nFor **negative** commands, use the present subjunctive: **No habléis** (don't speak!)\n\n📖 **Practice Makes Perfect** p.197",
        "nl": "De **vosotros** gebiedende wijs (gebruikt in Spanje voor informeel meervoud 'jullie') wordt gevormd door de laatste **-r** van het hele werkwoord te vervangen door **-d**:\n\n**hablar → hablad** (spreek!)\n**comer → comed** (eet!)\n**vivir → vivid** (leef!)\n\nVoor **ontkennende** gebiedende wijs gebruik je de subjunctivo: **No habléis** (spreek niet!)\n\n📖 **Practice Makes Perfect** p.197"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Regular Affirmative Tú Commands", "nl": "Regelmatige Bevestigende Tú Bevelen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "A regular affirmative command is formed by simply dropping the **s** from the second-person singular conjugated form:\n\n**Hablas** → **¡Habla!** (Speak!)\n**Comes** → **¡Come!** (Eat!)\n**Vives** → **¡Vive!** (Live!)",
        "nl": "Een regelmatig bevestigend bevel wordt gevormd door de **s** weg te laten van de tweede persoon enkelvoud:\n\n**Hablas** → **¡Habla!** (Spreek!)\n**Comes** → **¡Come!** (Eet!)\n**Vives** → **¡Vive!** (Leef!)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Regular Negative Tú Commands", "nl": "Regelmatige Ontkennende Tú Bevelen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "A regular negative command is formed as follows:\n1. Begin with the present tense first-person singular (**yo**) form.\n2. Remove the **-o** ending (the \"yo stem\").\n3. For **-ar** verbs, add **-es**. For **-er** and **-ir** verbs, add **-as**.\n\n**hablo** → **habl-** → **¡No hables!**\n**como** → **com-** → **¡No comas!**\n**escribo** → **escrib-** → **¡No escribas!**",
        "nl": "Een ontkennend bevel wordt als volgt gevormd:\n1. Begin met de eerste persoon enkelvoud (**yo**) vorm.\n2. Verwijder de **-o** uitgang.\n3. Voeg **-es** toe voor **-ar** werkwoorden, **-as** voor **-er** en **-ir** werkwoorden.\n\n**hablo** → **habl-** → **¡No hables!**\n**como** → **com-** → **¡No comas!**\n**escribo** → **escrib-** → **¡No escribas!**"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "rule_box",
      "title": { "en": "Spelling Changes & Positive vs Negative", "nl": "Spellingveranderingen & Positief vs Negatief" },
      "content": {
        "en": "Before the letter **e**, the following orthographic changes apply:\n• **c → qu** (No toques el piano!)\n• **g → gu** (No juegues al béisbol!)\n• **z → c** (No comiences!)\n\n**Positive (tú):** Mira, Visita, Compra, Estudia, Come, Bebe, Escribe, Llama\n**Negative (tú):** No mires, No visites, No compres, No estudies, No comas, No bebas, No escribas, No llames",
        "nl": "Vóór de letter **e** gelden de volgende spellingveranderingen:\n• **c → qu** (No toques el piano!)\n• **g → gu** (No juegues al béisbol!)\n• **z → c** (No comiences!)\n\n**Positief (tú):** Mira, Visita, Compra, Estudia, Come, Bebe, Escribe, Llama\n**Negatief (tú):** No mires, No visites, No compres, No estudies, No comas, No bebas, No escribas, No llames"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Irregular Tú Commands", "nl": "Onregelmatige Tú Bevelen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "There are very few verbs with irregular tú commands. Listed below are the most common:\n\n| Infinitive | Affirmative | Negative |\n|---|---|---|\n| decir | **di** | no digas |\n| hacer | **haz** | no hagas |\n| ir | **ve** | no vayas |\n| poner | **pon** | no pongas |\n| salir | **sal** | no salgas |\n| ser | **sé** | no seas |\n| tener | **ten** | no tengas |\n| venir | **ven** | no vengas |",
        "nl": "Er zijn slechts weinig werkwoorden met onregelmatige tú bevelen:\n\n| Infinitief | Bevestigend | Ontkennend |\n|---|---|---|\n| decir | **di** | no digas |\n| hacer | **haz** | no hagas |\n| ir | **ve** | no vayas |\n| poner | **pon** | no pongas |\n| salir | **sal** | no salgas |\n| ser | **sé** | no seas |\n| tener | **ten** | no tengas |\n| venir | **ven** | no vengas |"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Usted Commands", "nl": "Usted Bevelen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "Regular **usted** commands have a single form for both affirmative and negative:\n1. Begin with the present tense first-person singular (**yo**) form.\n2. Remove the **-o** ending (the \"yo stem\").\n3. For **-ar** verbs, add **-e**. For **-er** and **-ir** verbs, add **-a**.\n\n**hablo** → **habl-** → **¡Hable!** (Speak!)\n**como** → **com-** → **¡Coma!** (Eat!)\n**escribo** → **escrib-** → **¡Escriba!** (Write!)\n\nThere are only three irregular usted commands:\n• ir → **¡Vaya!** (Go!)\n• saber → **¡Sepa!** (Know!)\n• ser → **¡Sea!** (Be!)",
        "nl": "Regelmatige **usted** bevelen hebben één vorm voor zowel bevestigend als ontkennend:\n1. Begin met de eerste persoon enkelvoud (**yo**) vorm.\n2. Verwijder de **-o** uitgang.\n3. Voeg **-e** toe voor **-ar** werkwoorden, **-a** voor **-er** en **-ir** werkwoorden.\n\nEr zijn slechts drie onregelmatige usted bevelen: ir → **¡Vaya!**, saber → **¡Sepa!**, ser → **¡Sea!**"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Ustedes & Nosotros Commands", "nl": "Ustedes & Nosotros Bevelen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "**Ustedes** commands are nearly identical to usted commands, with **-n** added: **¡Hablen!** **¡Coman!** **¡Escriban!**\n\n**Nosotros** commands (\"let's...\"):\n1. Begin with the yo form, remove -o.\n2. For **-ar** verbs, add **-emos**. For **-er/-ir** verbs, add **-amos**.\n\n**¡Hablemos!** (Let's talk!) — **¡Comamos!** (Let's eat!) — **¡Escribamos!** (Let's write!)\n\nNegative: **¡No trabajemos!** (Let's not work!)\nIrregular: ir → **¡Vamos!** / **¡No vayamos!**",
        "nl": "**Ustedes** bevelen zijn bijna identiek aan usted bevelen, met **-n** toegevoegd: **¡Hablen!** **¡Coman!** **¡Escriban!**\n\n**Nosotros** bevelen (\"laten we...\"):\n1. Begin met de yo-vorm, verwijder -o.\n2. Voeg **-emos** toe voor -ar, **-amos** voor -er/-ir.\n\n**¡Hablemos!** (Laten we praten!) — **¡Comamos!** (Laten we eten!)\nOntkennend: **¡No trabajemos!** (Laten we niet werken!)"
      }
    }
  ],
